  <brief_title>Post - Hospital Syndrome: Profile of Functional Status by Malnutrition</brief_title>
  <official_title>Post-Hospital Syndrome: Evaluation of Functional Status in Malnourished, Geriatric Patients at Hospital Discharge</official_title>
  <sponsors>
